==Slovak==
===Cardinal numeral===
'''sedem''' ''or'' '''siedmi'''
# [[seven]] (7).

The word '''sedem''' is followed by a [[subject]] in [[genitive]] [[plural]]. The word '''[[siedmi]]''' can only be used to describe a group of seven men (male humans) and is followed by the [[masculine]] [[nominative]] [[plural]].

